<h2 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">Everything You Need to Know</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
<div class="row ">
<div class="span3 "><div class="extra-wrap serv">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Classes</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">At Atmosphere Academy, we pride ourselves in making all of our students rising stars. We want our students to be excited to learn. Atmosphere students have three Humanities (Reading, Writing, Social Studies) classes per day and two STEM (Math and Science) classes per day rotating classroom thru classroom in a high school model.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
<div class="list styled ok-circle-list">
<ul>
<li>
<strong>750 min</strong> English &amp; Social Studies/ week</li>
<li>
<strong>750 min</strong> Math &amp; Science / week</li>
<li>
<strong>Physical Education</strong> twice per week</li>
<li>
<strong>Health</strong> once per week</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
</div>
</div></div>
<div class="span3 "><div class="extra-wrap serv serv-1">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Our Location</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Since its existence in August 2015, Atmosphere Academy, a free public charter middle school, has been located at 22 Marble Hill Avenue in the Bronx. As of 2018, Atmosphere Academy has opened up two additional campuses within distance of Marble Hill Avenue.</p>
