<h3 style="text-align: center;">Our Program</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Atmosphere Academy provides its scholars with a Humanities and STEM curriculum designed to create college and career life skills within class sizes that provide the individualized attention our families are looking for. Atmosphere Academy not only supports the General Education population within District 10, but also serves scholars with various Special Education needs. Atmosphere Academy aims to help our scholars succeed by providing instruction throughout an extended school year and day.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
<div class="list styled ok-circle-list"><p style="text-align: center;"></p></div>
