<h3 style="text-align: center;">Enrichment Opportunities</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Atmosphere offers students a range of enrichment opportunities from foreign language to the arts to nature education. Through the creation of a highly engaging school setting, Atmosphere Academy not only prepares students to be ready for college, career, and life, but to succeed once they get there.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"></p>
<div class="list styled ok-circle-list">
<ul>
<li>Student Chosen Electives (Boxing, Foreign Language, the Arts, Drama Club, &amp; more)</li>
<li>Partnerships with organizations such as Westmoreland Sanctuary, Fluent City, and Westchester Land Trust provide scholars the opportunity to experience Nature Education</li>
<li>Career Exploration (Career X) allows students to explore various job opportunities</li>
<li>After-School Athletics (Soccer, Basketball, Flag Football, Volleyball, Softball, and Baseball)</li>
</ul>
